# Wallet Frontend (HTML/CSS/JS)

This is the frontend for the Django Wallet Application.

## Features

- User Signup/Login
- View Balance
- Enable Wallet
- View Transaction History

## Folder Structure

- `index.html`, `signup.html`, `login.html`, `dashboard.html`
- `css/styles.css`
- `js/api.js`, `auth.js`, `dashboard.js`

## How to Run

1. Host with Live Server or `python -m http.server`
2. Update `API_BASE` in `js/api.js` as per your backend (default: `localhost:8000`)
3. Ensure CORS is enabled on Django backend (`django-cors-headers`)

## Security

- Tokens stored in `localStorage`
- All APIs use Bearer Auth

## Backend Assumption

- JWT Token or DRF Token for auth
- `/api/signup/`, `/api/login/`, `/api/wallet/enable/`, `/api/wallet/balance/`, `/api/wallet/transactions/`
